s providing the unique permeability characteristics of Nafion membranes. In addition, we investigate the clustering and continuum percolation in the water phase, using the formalism of pair-connectedness correlation functions. The mean cluster size found theoretically is in reasonable agreement with the corresponding experimental estimates existing in the literature.},
